{"word":"Shield","slug":"shield","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Shield</b> Defensive armor.<br/> Different kinds of, designated as buckler, shield, target<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=35&verse=2'>Psa 35:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=38&verse=4'>Eze 38:4</a><br/> Used by:<br/> - Saul<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=1&verse=21'>2Sa 1:21</a> <br/> - The Benjamites<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=14&verse=8'>2Ch 14:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=17&verse=17'>2Ch 17:17</a> <br/> Uzziah equipped the children of Israel with<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=26&verse=14'>2Ch 26:14</a><br/> Made of:<br/> - Made of:<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=14&verse=27'>1Ki 14:27</a> <br/> - Gold<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=8&verse=7'>2Sa 8:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=10&verse=17'>1Ki 10:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=9&verse=16'>2Ch 9:16</a> <br/> - Wood<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=39&verse=10'>Eze 39:10</a> <br/> Made with bosses<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=15&verse=26'>Job 15:26</a><br/> Stored in:<br/> - Armories<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=10&verse=17'>2Ki 10:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=11&verse=12'>2Ch 11:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=32&verse=5'>2Ch 32:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=32&verse=27'>2Ch 32:27</a> <br/> - The tabernacle<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=11&verse=10'>2Ki 11:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=23&verse=9'>2Ch 23:9</a> <br/> Covered when not in use<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=22&verse=6'>Isa 22:6</a><br/> Painted red<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=34&chapter=2&verse=3'>Nah 2:3</a><br/><a href='S:Arms'>Arms</a><br/> Figurative:<br/> - Of God's protection<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=15&verse=1'>Gen 15:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=33&verse=29'>Deu 33:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=22&verse=3'>2Sa 22:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=22&verse=36'>2Sa 22:36</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=5&verse=12'>Psa 5:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=18&verse=2'>Psa 18:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=18&verse=35'>Psa 18:35</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=33&verse=20'>Psa 33:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=59&verse=11'>Psa 59:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=84&verse=9'>Psa 84:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=84&verse=11'>Psa 84:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=89&verse=18'>Psa 89:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=30&verse=5'>Pro 30:5</a> <br/> - Of God's truth<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=91&verse=4'>Psa 91:4</a> <br/> - Of an entire army<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=46&verse=3'>Jer 46:3</a> "}]}